              ans[k]=nums1[i];\\n                i++;\\n            }else{\\n                ans[k]=nums2[j];\\n                j++;\\n            }\\n            k++;\\n        }\\n        while(j<n){\\n            ans[k]=nums2[j];\\n            j++;k++;\\n        }\\n        while(i<m){\\n            ans[k]=nums1[i];\\n            k++;i++;\\n        }\\n        for(int x = 0; x < m+n; x++){ \\n            nums1[x] = ans[x];\\n        } // because we\'ve to copy it to nums1 array only \\n    }\\n}","compare_result":"11111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111","title_slug":"merge-sorted-array","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1,"frontend_id":761},{"id":2009045411,"question_id":88,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1\xc2\xa0month, 1\xc2\xa0week","timestamp":1779368542,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"0 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/2009045411/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Merge Sorted Array","memory":"43.6 MB","code":"class Solution {\\n    public void merge(int[] nums1, int m, int[] nums2, int n) {\\n        while(m > 0 && n > 0){\\n            //compare and place\\n            if(nums1[m-1] >= nums2[n-1]){\\n                nums1[m+n - 1] = nums1[m-1];\\n                m--;\\n            }else{\\n                nums1[m+n - 1] = nums2[n-1];\\n                n--;\\n            }\\n        }\\n\\n        while(n > 0){\\n            //place remaining of nums 2\\n            nums1[m+n - 1] = nums2[n-1];\\n            n--;\\n        }\\n    }\\n}","compare_result":"11111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111","title_slug":"merge-sorted-array","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1,"frontend_id":760},{"id":2008740982,"question_id":3329,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1\xc2\xa0month, 1\xc2\xa0week","timestamp":1779342672,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"187 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/2008740982/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Find the Length of the Longest Common Prefix","memory":"87.3 MB","code":"class Solution {\\n    public int longestCommonPrefix(int[] arr1, int[] arr2) {\\n        int maxCount = 0;\\n        Set<String> prefixes = new HashSet<>();\\n        for (int num : arr1) {\\n            String s = Integer.toString(num);\\n            StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();\\n            for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {\\n                sb.append(c);\\n                prefixes.add(sb.toString());\\n            }\\n        }\\n\\n        for (int i = 0; i < arr2.length; i++) {\\n            String s = Integer.toString(arr2[i]);\\n            StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();\\n            int curr = 0;\\n            for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {\\n                sb.append(c);\\n                if(prefixes.contains(sb.toString())){curr++;}else{break;}\\n                maxCount = Math.max(maxCount,curr);\\n            }\\n        }\\n        return maxCount;\\n    }\\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"find-the-length-of-the-longest-common-prefix","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1,"frontend_id":759}],"has_next":true,"last_key":""}'
